In *One Piece*, "the Pirate King" represents **Luffy’s promise** to his crew—to become the strongest pirate and fulfill his dream of finding the One Piece treasure. This vow binds the Straw Hats together, symbolizing their shared goal and loyalty. While adventure and freedom are themes, the title itself is tied to his oath.
